550
00:32:35,036 --> 00:32:36,496
I was blinded by the gold.

551
00:32:38,582 --> 00:32:40,417
She gave me these one-kilo bars.

552
00:32:40,500 --> 00:32:42,002
She asked me to sell them for her.

553
00:32:43,795 --> 00:32:45,589
Said I could keep one out of ten.

554
00:32:47,883 --> 00:32:48,967
Who is she?

555
00:32:51,178 --> 00:32:52,554
I don't know her name, sir.

556
00:32:52,637 --> 00:32:54,472
Do you think I'm fucking stupid?

557
00:32:56,892 --> 00:32:57,893
