N--no.

574
00:33:47,984 --> 00:33:49,152
No.

575
00:33:49,236 --> 00:33:50,862
[whimpers and swallows]

576
00:33:51,363 --> 00:33:52,697
It's not Kim Heeju?

577
00:33:53,949 --> 00:33:55,116
No.

578
00:33:59,579 --> 00:34:01,623
You told me you didn't know her name.

579
00:34:02,457 --> 00:34:03,959
