580
00:34:06,044 --> 00:34:07,545
I...

581
00:34:07,629 --> 00:34:09,589
[breathing heavily]

582
00:34:09,673 --> 00:34:11,633
- [Woogy groans]
- Fucker.

583
00:34:12,217 --> 00:34:13,343
