I really don't know!

584
00:34:13,426 --> 00:34:14,427
[blow lands]
[screaming]

585
00:34:14,511 --> 00:34:16,471
[wailing and crying]

586
00:34:16,554 --> 00:34:17,639
[blow lands]

587
00:34:17,722 --> 00:34:20,725
[Woogy sobbing]

588
00:34:21,768 --> 00:34:22,894
Hey, hey, hey, hey!

589
00:34:22,978 --> 00:34:25,397
[screaming]

590
00:34:26,815 --> 00:34:28,066
Hey, Director Park.

591
00:34:28,149 --> 00:34:29,442
I looked into Kim Heeju.

592
00:34:29,859 --> 00:34:31,361
I texted you her background check.

593
00:34:31,945 --> 00:34:33,196
And I pulled her phone records.

594
00:34:33,697 --> 00:34:35,407
[Kang] <i>Looks like her phone</i>
<i>is currently off.</i>

595
00:34:36,116 --> 00:34:38,576
<i>There's no call activity</i>
<i>for the past few days, either.</i>

596
00:34:39,494 --> 00:34:41,413
