601
00:34:52,757 --> 00:34:56,219
[Kang] <i>Uh, yeah, you know, the area</i>
<i>along Route 6 with the warehouses.</i>

602
00:34:56,303 --> 00:34:59,389
- <i>The redevelopment area.</i>
- Huh.

603
00:34:59,472 --> 00:35:03,727
And also on Bukju street in Jeongsan.
The Haengbok Pawnshop, too.

604
00:35:05,103 --> 00:35:06,813
Can you check out the industrial complex?

605
00:35:06,896 --> 00:35:08,231
