647
00:37:17,569 --> 00:37:18,653
GANGWON CENTRAL POLICE AGENCY
INVESTIGATIONS DIVISION

648
00:37:18,737 --> 00:37:19,821
DETECTIVE KANG DONGHOON

649
00:37:20,780 --> 00:37:21,781
Uh-huh.

650
00:37:24,826 --> 00:37:28,037
