- [Boy] Freeze!

671
00:39:11,182 --> 00:39:12,183
Ah!

672
00:39:12,267 --> 00:39:13,434
[children breathing heavily]

673
00:39:13,977 --> 00:39:15,520
[Girl B] Ah! Freeze!

674
00:39:16,354 --> 00:39:17,605
