675
00:39:17,689 --> 00:39:18,898
[Child] Gonna get you!

676
00:39:18,982 --> 00:39:20,233
[all laughing]

677
00:39:20,316 --> 00:39:22,110
- [girl screams]
- [Child] Freeze!

678
00:39:22,193 --> 00:39:25,196
[laughing continues]

679
00:39:25,822 --> 00:39:27,115
[Child] Come here!

680
00:39:27,198 --> 00:39:28,783
[laughter]

681
00:39:28,867 --> 00:39:30,785
[Child] Stop it!
Get away from me!

682
00:39:31,578 --> 00:39:34,080
[Mother A] <i>Hyewon. That's enough.</i>

683
00:39:34,163 --> 00:39:36,916
<i>Dinner's ready.</i>
<i>Your food's getting cold.</i>

684
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:40,003
[Mother B] <i>Minu, let's go home!</i>
<i>Come on. It's time for dinner.</i>

685
00:39:41,337 --> 00:39:44,173
[Mother C] <i>I can't believe this.</i>
<i>You little rascal.</i>

686
00:39:44,257 --> 00:39:46,885
<i>Where have you been?</i>
<i>I was worried sick!</i>

687
00:39:46,968 --> 00:39:48,678
[light buzzing]

688
00:39:48,761 --> 00:39:50,179
[Young Heeju] Mongsil!

689
00:39:50,263 --> 00:39:52,432
[breathing heavily]

690
00:39:58,271 --> 00:40:02,066
[crickets chirping]

691
00:40:04,235 --> 00:40:05,612
