692
00:40:06,154 --> 00:40:07,655
'Cause I'm frozen here.

693
00:40:08,072 --> 00:40:09,407
Everybody else went home.

694
00:40:09,490 --> 00:40:10,700
You better go, too.

695
00:40:11,159 --> 00:40:13,036
