698
00:40:16,873 --> 00:40:18,082
There are ghosts here.

699
00:40:20,710 --> 00:40:21,920
Tag me free.

700
00:40:23,046 --> 00:40:24,047
You do it!

701
00:40:24,839 --> 00:40:26,257
[Young Woogy] <i>You tag me!</i>

702
00:40:27,300 --> 00:40:29,010
[engine revving]

703
00:40:29,093 --> 00:40:31,095
[tires squealing]

704
00:40:31,179 --> 00:40:33,473
