705
00:40:36,893 --> 00:40:39,395
[creaking]

706
00:40:40,480 --> 00:40:43,483
[Heeju groaning]

707
00:40:58,247 --> 00:40:59,290
Woogy!

708
00:40:59,916 --> 00:41:01,459
[Woogy groaning]

709
00:41:03,753 --> 00:41:06,756
[strained breathing]

710
00:41:08,758 --> 00:41:10,009
Woogy?

711
00:41:10,301 --> 00:41:11,344
Heeju?

712
00:41:13,304 --> 00:41:14,555
Heeju.

713
00:41:15,139 --> 00:41:18,142
