717
00:41:28,111 --> 00:41:30,113
- [Heeju] Oh! It worked! Yes.
- You got it? You got it?

718
00:41:31,739 --> 00:41:32,991
What--how do I...

719
00:41:33,658 --> 00:41:35,535
[Woogy] Hey. There.

720
00:41:35,618 --> 00:41:36,786
Shoot.

721
00:41:37,412 --> 00:41:38,746
- [Heeju whimpers]
- [Woogy] There.

722
00:41:38,830 --> 00:41:40,164
[Heeju shouts]
[gun fires]

723
00:41:41,082 --> 00:41:42,750
- [whimpering]
- There, there, there. Shoot. Shoot.

724
00:41:42,834 --> 00:41:45,294
Kill him. There. There.

725
00:41:45,378 --> 00:41:46,546
[whimpering]

726
00:41:48,881 --> 00:41:50,091
[gunshot]

727
00:41:52,885 --> 00:41:55,179
[panicked breathing]

728
00:42:01,561 --> 00:42:04,564
[tires squealing]

729
00:42:16,993 --> 00:42:19,996
[♪ tense music]

730
00:42:26,252 --> 00:42:27,545
[keyboard clacking]

731
00:42:27,628 --> 00:42:29,338
PATIENT NAME: KIM HEEJU
NO PATIENTS MATCH THE SEARCH CRITERIA.

732
00:42:32,550 --> 00:42:35,553
We don't have anyone named Kim Heeju here.

733
00:42:36,054 --> 00:42:37,305
Ju Haran, then.

734
00:42:38,181 --> 00:42:39,724
Ju Haran.

735
00:42:39,807 --> 00:42:41,934
[keyboard clacking]

736
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:43,811
I'm sorry.

737
00:42:45,813 --> 00:42:47,315
A guardian, maybe?

738
00:42:47,398 --> 00:42:48,816
What about a guardian?

739
00:42:49,609 --> 00:42:51,235
Kim Heeju or Ju Haran.

740
00:42:52,111 --> 00:42:55,031
[engine rumbling]

741
00:42:55,114 --> 00:42:58,034
[engine groaning]

742
00:42:58,117 --> 00:43:01,120
[crickets chirping]

743
00:43:02,747 --> 00:43:05,750
[rattling]

744
00:43:08,836 --> 00:43:09,837
[engine hissing]

745
00:43:10,671 --> 00:43:12,465
[Heeju] What?

746
00:43:12,548 --> 00:43:13,925
What now?

747
00:43:17,011 --> 00:43:20,014
[breathing heavily]

748
00:43:21,265 --> 00:43:22,433
[Heeju] What?

749
00:43:22,517 --> 00:43:24,018
[exhales]

750
00:43:26,771 --> 00:43:28,106
Ah, shit.

751
00:43:30,358 --> 00:43:33,361
[mask hissing]

752
00:44:01,681 --> 00:44:04,684
[♪ suspenseful music]

753
00:44:09,397 --> 00:44:13,359
CALLS

754
00:44:16,070 --> 00:44:18,197
HEEJU

755
00:44:19,073 --> 00:44:22,118
[Operator] <i>Your call has been forwarded</i>
<i>to an automated voice messaging system.</i>

756
00:44:22,201 --> 00:44:24,036
<i>The number you have dial--</i>
[phone disconnects]

757
00:44:33,421 --> 00:44:35,047
KIM HEEJU

758
00:44:35,131 --> 00:44:36,757
[crickets chirping]

759
00:44:36,841 --> 00:44:39,218
- [Heeju inhales and exhales]
- [Woogy] Where are we?

760
00:44:39,886 --> 00:44:42,138
Huh? Not the pawnshop, right?

761
00:44:42,638 --> 00:44:43,639
We can't go there.

762
00:44:44,223 --> 00:44:45,349
I know.

763
00:44:46,976 --> 00:44:49,061
I was on the way to the workshop.

764
00:44:49,395 --> 00:44:50,688
